## Scrolling the page:

ctrl+u/ctrl+d for scrolling half a page of text
-ctrl+f/ctrl+b for scrolling by a full page of text

gg to jump to top of the file
G to jump to bottom of the file

jumping to line:
: 100 G to jump to  line 100

go back to place you jumped from: ctrl+o
undo cltr+o: ctlr+ i


buffers:
close buffer: type :bd to close current buffer

